''ASUS'''s firmware indicates used of a [[Ralink]]/[[TrendChip]] SoC
===Overview=== *True two-in-one modem router with both Ethernet and DSL :internet connection (WAN) ports *Dual-purpose design offers more performance and flexibility :for wired and wireless connections *ASUSWRT Dashboard user interface for easy setup, signal :monitoring and network application control *File and printer sharing via two multi-functional USB ports
===Specifications=== :per ''ASUS'''s product page *Antenna: 3x detachable antenna (2dBi) *Ports: xDSL: 1x ADSL2+ (RJ11) :WAN: 1x GbE (RJ45) 10/100/1000 BaseT :LAN: 4x GbE (RJ45) 10/100/1000 BaseT :USB: 2x USB 2.0 *Power Adapter: :AC Input : 100~240V (50~60HZ) :DC Output : 12V / 2A *Dimensions (W x H x D): [[Dimensions::207 mm x 35.5 mm x 148.8 mm]] *Weight: [[Weight::500 g]]
